{
  "stem": "20684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but a lot of our partisans got caught, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it went both ways.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people disappeared and they got killed, so that's that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that went on like that for a couple of winters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Two-- two events that stood out most of all, except my usual work, was there was at one stage a very, very heavy bombing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was towards the end of the war, as it happened, and the retreating German soldiers going to the forest and the Russians were bombing the hell out of them and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the Germans were bombing, the Russians were bombing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was really what they were retreating from, the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a terrible night one night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was sitting on a tree.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the morning, I came down, there was lots of wounded and killed partisans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody was very sad, very sad because many of their friends were just blown up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in a lucky tree, I had a lucky run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I came down from the tree, I found a leg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was winter-- winter of '45, the last winter we spent in the forest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I found a leg which was a little--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Winter.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which was the last winter I spent?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, yes, because [INAUDIBLE] Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Winter of '44, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm dreaming, pardon me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I found a leg which was my size, still had a boot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know who it belonged to because the rest was blown up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I got that leg and I was trying to tell the officer that I'm taking that leg to my father, who was about 300 meters away in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and he was very upset.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I couldn't understand why.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
